==Sequel==
A sequel, ''[[Ocho apellidos catalanes]]'' ({{lang-en|Eight Catalan Surnames}}) was released on 20 November 2015. [[Emilio Martínez-Lázaro]] repeated as director and [[Borja Cobeaga]] and Diego San José repeated as screenwriters. The original cast was joined by [[Berto Romero]], [[Rosa Maria Sardà]] and Belén Cuesta.<ref>{{cite web|author=El País|title=‘Ocho apellidos catalanes’ se estrenará el 20 de noviembre|url=http://cultura.elpais.com/cultura/2015/07/09/actualidad/1436439163_784701.html}}</ref>

